description:
#### New package name: **[transmission](https://chocolatey.org/packages/transmission)**

---

`transmission-qt` has been deprecated because of [Chocolatey naming conventions](https://www.chocolatey.org/docs/create-packages#naming-your-package) and this unofficial build is no longer being developed because an official build is now available from the Transmission Project.

This package exists only for backward compatibility to provide a transitional, empty, dummy package for existing users and scripts which may still use this package ID.
summary: [Deprecated] Unofficial port of Transmission-Qt to Windows
author: Transmission Project
